
// This Hyperlambda code snippet opens an ODBC database connection using a connection string named "generic" and a database named "appdata". It then executes a SQL query to retrieve a scalar value from the "settings" table where the "key" is 'site-title', returning the result as a single value.
odbc.connect:[generic|appdata]
   odbc.scalar:"select value from settings where key = 'site-title'"
